this site will allow readers to submit any English-language text into the open field above. This text will then be syntactically matched with sections of the 500-line  source poem, “<a href=\"http://www.zombiepoetryproject.com/zombie-ride-along/\">Zombie Ride-Along</a>” to produce a new “zombified” poem of random lineation. The new poem will be added to the growing anthology archived on this site.','','','inherit','closed','closed','','76-revision-v1','','','2015-10-13 14:38:08','2015-10-13 14:38:08','',76,'http://www.zombiepoetryproject.com/2015/10/13/76-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
